00058         void begin()
00059         {
00060             m_current = (T*)m_head.QPeek();
00061         }
00062         void back()
00063         {
00064             m_current = (T*)m_head.QBack();
00065         }
00066         bool end()
00067         {
00068             return (m_current == (T*)m_head.Self());

00071         {

00073         }
00074         T* operator*()

00076             return m_current;
00077         }

00079         {
00080             m_current = (T*)m_current->QPeek();
00081             return *this;
00082         }
00083         _myT& operator--()
00084         {
00085             // no check on NULL! make sure you don't try to increment beyond end
00086             m_current = (T*)m_current->QBack();

00109     {
00110         if (!item->QEmpty())

00112         item->m_bqlink = m_bqlink;

00130         if (QEmpty())

00134         SG_QList* item = m_fqlink;
00135         m_fqlink = item->m_fqlink;
